    "Computers belonging to all users are therefore resource suppliers as well as consumers.",
    "Each block in a blockchain created by the blockchain has a series of transactions that take place at a given moment.",
    "With a P2P design, this data structure can be expanded and shared by numerous clients.",
    "Every network node in a peer-to-peer network is linked to every other network node.",
    "These are the nodes that assist with block storage and mine blocks in accordance with the parameters outlined in the blockchain algorithm."
